summary: An Ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit to condemn private property for the laying off, extending, widening and establishing of Walcott Street, from 54th Avenue South to a point six hundred (600) feet more or less easterly from the east margin of 55th Avenue South, under Ordinance No. 35827, Cause No. 118,547, insofar as the same affects certain property in Blocks Thirteen (13), Fourteen (14) and Fifteen (15), C. D. Hillman's Atlantic City Addition to the City of Seattle.
